Description: terminal-based incident response space horror game
 Eidolon Drift is a curses-based adventure game in which the player takes
 the role of an incident responder aboard a distressed spaceship. Navigate
 through the vessel, reach the Command Module, and escape via the emergency
 pod while managing a deteriorating sanity level.
 .
 Features procedural map generation, a sanity system that shrinks the
 visible field of view, atmospheric ambient messages, and multiple colour
 themes (dark, retro, high-contrast).
